{"tid":930812,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新盤低開】觀月‧樺峰即劈「1球」 麗港城睇樓客全褪軚","createTime":"2018-12-06T14:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T09:39:29.000Z","uid":174649,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"571d72ebc1ff3a7879709a0ab7d602512ec4810c","tid":930812,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T14:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181206/large/1544098457_1815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181206%2Flarge%2F1544098457_1815.jpg&h=a809671f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n信置(083)觀塘裕民坊重建項目凱滙一期低價開售，首批折實平均呎價1.73萬元，較鄰區啟德新盤平近三成，亦較裕民坊第一期重建項目觀月‧樺峰二手平均呎價1.8萬元為低。區內代理相信，新盤低開，短期東九龍以至將軍澳二手交投勢陷凍封，「新盤都咁平，二手仲邊有人買」，同區二手樓價料跌一至兩成。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，麗港城本周末原有六組客預約睇樓，現在已經全部「甩底」，「啲客去晒凱滙」。二手業主開始劈價，觀月‧樺峰中低層B室兩房戶，實用面積560方呎，原叫價1,050萬元，業主見凱滙低開後，今日叫價即劈百萬至900萬元，呎價16,071元。<br />\n麗港城亦有減價求售情況，為7座中層兩房戶，實用面積517方呎，原叫價750萬元，今日劈到690萬元，呎價13,346元平過凱滙仍無人問津。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42abae4e93d804e1b3025be9378c49bf6ad97756","tid":930812,"uid":83582,"like":38,"dislike":8,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"信和累街坊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181ff9acf63c9558d536032daf15236b19e3774b","tid":930812,"uid":195728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"新盤第一滴血"},{"pid":"9f74374262569d4199e389b68f551e3bf2030a00","tid":930812,"uid":28245,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:19:15.000Z","msg":"今次除左將軍澳冧市 應該到到都劈2成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過埋年 貿易戰談判破裂"},{"pid":"7b5eb863d45c580dc05bb319f01d